# ripgrep sweep scope (memory Policy): docs/ surveys stay out of root-wide
# rg/Grep-tool searches. Deliberate docs searches: `git grep <pat> -- docs/`,
# `rg --no-ignore`, or explicit file paths. Read access is unaffected.
# .rgignore, not .ignore: Marksman reads .ignore and would drop docs/*.md
# from its link index (false "non-existent document" warnings).
docs/
